    <briefdescription>
<para>LoRaWAN join parameters for over-the-Air activation (OTAA) </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Note that all of the fields use LoRaWAN 1.1 terminology.</para>
<para>All parameters are optional if a secure element is present in which case the values stored in the secure element will be used instead. </para>
